  "test": {
    "runner": "VSTest"
  }
}
```

No SDK version pinned, so it uses the latest installed SDK (11.0.100-preview.3). Maybe the preview SDK handles `net8.0-windows` differently. Let me try pinning to .NET 8 SDK.

Actually, wait. The baseline built fine with this same SDK. The issue is only after my changes. Let me narrow down what exactly causes this. Let me test without OutputType=Exe.

